file_content.text: You are the most beautiful woman I've ever--what are you doing? Don't let me die again!
What are you waiting for? Use the dream-rock.
I'm ready if you are, Gormak. This is the nightmare.
It's time for you to bleed, ghost. Use the dream-rock, Gormak.
I am trying. Corruption is strong here. Hard to fight.
What, no sense of humor? You won't beat me that easily!
You're the Sith who killed Darth Skotia! Amazing!
Can I tell you something personal? You are the most beautiful woman I've ever known. I love you. But you must die.
